Dr. Kamga continues to actively participate in numerous transportation-related projects at UTRC.   
His research interests include: intelligent transportation system; modeling and traffic simulation;   
analysis of very large transportation networks; use of real-time information for travel;   
transportation modeling using mobile sensors; transportation planning and policy, transportation operations; sustainability and environment; and transportation safety.
